                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec nunc nisl, rutrum eget ex in, cursus sagittis elit. Proin consequat uatril tum blandit. Susp endisse tempus pharetra celerisque. Vivamus finibus eu justo et mattis."
